data.description: see this beautiful Brick Bungalow  for yourself! It won't be long before it's gone! This beautiful home is in move in ready condition for your family to enjoy. On the main floor, the home features 3 bedrooms, dining room and living room with beautiful hard wood floors.  kitchen with quartz counter tops, tile floors, and stainless-steel appliances. The home features an upstairs spacious unfinished attic ready for all your Ideas.  huge finished basement with a bar ready for all your family gatherings, basement also includes a laundry area with a full bathroom. 2-car garage is in great condition, and an overhead door front and back, perfect for outdoor entertaining.  Schedule your visit today!
